longBusinessSummary: Cycurion, Inc. provides network communications and information technology security solutions. The company provides consulting and advisory services, such as security control assessments, risk management and compliance audits, cybersecurity awareness and training, virtual CISO support, security architecture and engineering, staff augmentation, cloud security, and digital modernization. It offers managed IT services, which include project management and IV&V, network infrastructure, voice and data infrastructure engineering and management, IT help desk support, HW/SW license management, systems engineering and administration, application development, and staff augmentation. In addition, the company provides managed security services including managed detection and response, end point detection and response, threat and vulnerability management, 24/7/365 security monitoring, external attack surface management, firewall management, vulnerability and penetration testing, digital forensic and incident response, and threat hunting and threat intelligence. Further, it offers ARx platform, a turnkey web application protection and managed security solution that combines all the essential cybersecurity layers. It offers solutions to enterprise businesses, small and medium businesses, government agencies, healthcare, and higher education industries. Cycurion, Inc. is based in McLean, Virginia.
